modName: Half Dryad-Elf Race english - polish ENG - PL - CBBE UNP UNPB ADEC
summary: New races Half Dryad-Elf. It is a combination of Dryad and Wood Elf.
descriptionHtml:
[size=4][color=teal]Short Info:[/color][/size]

Hi all, sorry for my poor english. This is my first mod, please be understanding

[size=5]At the outset I would like to thank all those who endorsement my mod. I wish you a lot of fun with this mod[/size]

This mod It is a combination of Dryad and Wood Elf. Mod mainly based on [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/21458]Dryad Race[/url]. I added and changed racial skills. I changed the texture of the form. Changes in armory. Mod designed for the female form.

MOD uses CBBE body model. Due to problems with the conversion of the UNP for CBBE, armor are still UNP format. However, the modeling of the body via Bodyslide, allows use of armor CBBE or UNP. If you do not mix different pieces of armor of the two models, it should all look good.

If you notice any errors please contact with me. Any suggestions are welcome. 

[size=4][color=red]New changes:[/color][/size]
Added in optional file support for some body (CBBE Calientes v3.2,  CBBE MAK, UNP, UNPB, ADEC) - only body, not for Dryad armor is still UNP

[size=5][color=lime]Please read thise before install or upgrade mod:[/color][/size]

I\'m sorry for the inconvenience during this transition, but the aim was to facilitate my work, reducing the installation footprint, compatibility with other mods especially my second mod \'Liza Half-Elf Dryad Companion \".

First, before you install the mod to version 1.8 or higher, please uninstall previous versions of the mod.

Second, if you are just beginning to fun with this mod, and you create a new character just does not need to read further. In this situation, everything is OK.
However, if you have a save game using this mod you have to choose a race again. Please enter the console using the tilde key on the keyboard (~) and type the command \"showracemenu\". You will get the character creation menu. You have to re-select the Half-Elf Dryad race.
[color=green]
Instead of using the \"showracemenu\", I recommend you use the mod [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/9458]Ring of Change - ShowRaceMenu Fix[/url] by GoroUnreal (or [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/26377]Ring of Change - Showracemenu Fix - polish translation[/url] by Siaalonas. There are very good scrrenshots where to look for the ring.). In my case, when a large amount of mods have command it crashed. I had to turn off all the mods to change the race. This mod allows you to change the race quickly and easily without excluding other mods. You just have to find another race and select  then reselect Half Dryad-Efl Race, remove ring and you\'re done.
[/color]
If you had a suit of armor from this mod is a must forge her again.

If you do not use and was not interested in my other companion mod for mod then you can upgrade to version 1.7. It contains the same changes as version 1.8, except that it does not work with the mod lysed Half-Elf Dryad Companion version 1.3 and does not have a compressed folder. Using version 1.7 you will not have to use the endorsement \"showracemenu\". But keep this in mind that all subsequent changes will be based on version 1.8.

[size=4][color=red]Requirements:[/color][/size]
MOD should not require other MODs. However, if you have problems install [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24168]RaceCompatibility[/url]. At the time of creation I was based on ver. 1.50 Vanilla this mod . I make all updates on the latest version.
My version of the game is 1.9.32.0 with DLC Dawnguard and Dragonborn. Mod was created on game ver. 1.8.52.0 without any DLC. Therefore, it should be compatible with different versions of the game

[size=4][color=yellow]Highly Recommended to use this mods:[/color][/size]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/26800]XP32 Maximum Skeleton -XPMS[/url] by xp32
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/18110]Hair packs of TES IV Oblivion for Female Only[/url] by Radioragae
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/12101] Armor from Spriggan Wood _ Sexy lore friendly CBBE armor[/url] by Nalim

[size=4][color=aqua]Optional mod:[/color][/size]
I recommend my other mod [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/33483]Lizia Half Dryad-Elf Companion[/url]

[size=4][color=green]Skill Bonuses[/color][/size]
- Restoration: 10
- Conjuration 10
- Archery 10
- One-Handed 5

[size=4][color=green]Attributes[/color][/size]
- Starting Health: 50
- Starting Magicka: 60
- Starting Stamina: 50
- Health Regen: 0.7
- Magicka Regen: 5.0
- Stamina Regen: 3.0
- Base Carry Weight 350

[size=4][color=green]Spells & abilities[/color][/size]
- Wooden Skin (Ability): Resist Damage 10%
- Root (Lesser Power): Root 15 seconds
- Tree Link (Lesser Power): Over 60s increases your Health regeneration to 3.85, Magicka ito 10.0 and stamina to 8.0
- Dragon\'s Blood Armor (Lesser Power): It gives 80% resistance to physical damage(Dragonhide effect) and 20% of the remaining resistance.
- Summon Etheral Horse (Lesser Power): Summon Etheral Horse for 60s
- Summon Spriggan (Lesser Power): Summon Spriggan for 3m 
- Magic Bow (Lesser Power): Summon Etheral Bow
- Magic Sword (Leser Power): Summon Etheral Sword
- LIght (Lesser Power): Effect Candlelight
- Command Animal (Power): Same effect what have wooden elf
- Allow combat on Mount
- All Spriggan are your friends and they will not attack you
